\id PHM - Dawro
\h Pilimoona
\toc3 Fim
\toc2 Pilimoona
\toc1 Pilimoona
\mt2 Phawuloosi
\mt1 Pilimoonaw
\mt2 Xaafeedda Kiitaa
\imt1 Geluwaa
\ip Pilimooni eretteedda ammaniyaa asa; I Qolaasiyaasa woosa golliya asa gidennaan waayyii aggana. Pilimoonaw Anaasimoosa giya ayllii de7ee. He ayllii bare godaappe betiide beedda wode, qasho gollen de7iyaa Phawuloosanna gaketteedda. Anaasimoosi Phawuloosa bagganna Yesuusa ammaneedda. Phawuloosi Pilimoonassi xaafeedda kiitay Pilimooni guyye simmi biidde de7iyaa bare qoomaanna sigettanaadan, hewaa hassayissiyawaa. Hewaa bollaakka ha77i Anaasimoosi ammaniyaa asa gideedda diraw, hawaappe sinthaw ammaniyaa ishaadan A mokki akkanaappe attin, qoomaadan A xeellenaadan aw odee.
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatuwassi Imetteedda Qantha Qofatuwaa
\io1 Geluwaa (1-3)
\io1 Pilimoonassi Phawuloosa galataa (4-7)
\io1 Phawuloosi Anasimoosa diraw shiishsheedda mino ooshaa (8-22)
\io1 Wurssethaa qutiyaa (23-25)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Taani Phawuloosi, Yesuusi Kiristtoosa diraw qashuwan de7iyaawenne nu ishaa Ximootoosi, nuunanna oothiyaa nuuni siiqiyaa Pilimoonaw,
\v 2 ne gollen shiiqiyaa ammaniyaawanttoo, nu michchatti Afibissinne nuunanna ittippe de7iyaa Kiristtoosa wottaaddaraa Arkkipoosaw ha dabidaabbiyaa xaafeetto. \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Qol 4:17\x*
\p 
\v 3 Xoossaa nu Aawuwaappenne nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosappe aadho keekatethaynne sarotethay hinttenttussi gido.
\s1 Pilimoona Siiquwaanne Ammanuwaa
\p 
\v 4-5 Neeni Xoossaa asatuwaa siiqiyaawaanne Godaa Yesuusa ammaniyaawaa taani sisiyaa diraw, Xoossaa woossaade neena hassayiya wode ubbaan, ta Xoossaa galatay.
\v 6 Neeni ne ammanuwaa haratuwaanna shaakkiyaawe nuussi Kiristtoosi Yesuusa bagganna yiyaa lo77obaa ubbaa erissana mala, taani Xoossaa woossay.
\v 7 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa asatuwaa wozanay ne kiitaan minneedda diraw, ta ishaw, taani ne siiquwan daro nashechchaanne menthethuwaa demmaaddi.
\s1 Anaasimoosi Pilimoonakko Simmeedda Simuwaa
\p 
\v 8 Hewaa diraw, neeni oothanaw bessiyaawaa oothana mala, taani neena azazanaw Kiristtoosa bagganna xalooppekka,
\v 9 Taani Phawuloosi cimeeddawe, Kiristtoosi Yesuusaw ha77ikka qashuwan de7iyaawe, siiquwaa diraw, neena woossay.
\v 10 Taani qashuwan de7aadde aw aawuwaa gideedda ta na7aa Anaasimoosa \f + \fr 1:10 \fq Anaasimoosa: \ft Giyaa sunthaa bilethay, Griikiyaa qaalaan go77iyaawaa woy maaddiyaawaa guussaa.\f* diraw, neena woossay. \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Qol 4:9\x*
\v 11 I kase neena go77enna; shin ha77i neenakka taanakka tumu go77ee.
\p 
\v 12-13 Taani wozanappe dosiyaa Anaasimoosa neekko yeddowe ta wozanaa yeddowaa. Taani wonggalaa diraw qashetta utta de7ishshin, neena kochchiide, taana maaddana mala, ta matan A ashshanaw koyyay.
\v 14 Shin neeni ne sheniyaadan oothanaawaa koyyayppe attin, neenanna zorettennan wolqqan aynne oothanaw koyyikke.
\p 
\v 15 Anaasimoosi guutha wodiyaa neeppe shaaketteeddawe, ooni eri simmiide, ubba wodekka neenanna de7anaassenttonne.
\v 16 Simmi hawaappe sinthaw Anaasimoosi aylliya gidenna; shin aylliyaappe I loythi aadhdhee; I taw ay keena siiqo ishee! Qassi I new asaa baggaannakka Godaa baggaannakka ay keena aadhdheedda ishaa gidanddeeshsha!
\p 
\v 17 Simmi neeni taana ne laggethaa giyaawaa gidooppe, taana mokkiyaawaadan, A mokka.
\v 18 I new bayizzeeddabay woy A bolla new acuu de7ooppe, taappe cigaa akka.
\v 19 He acuwaa taani ciggana gaade, taani Phawuloosi ta kushiyan xaafay. Neeni taw ne shemppuwaa acota utteeddawaa taani neena hassayissanaw koshshenna.
\p 
\v 20 E, ta ishaw, Godaa bagganna neeppe maaduwaa demmanaw koyyay. Kiristtoosa bagganna taana menthetha.
\v 21 Taani geeddawaappe daruwaa neeni oothanaawaa eraade, qassi ne taw azazettanawaakka ammanaade, hawaa new xaafay.
\p 
\v 22 Qassi hinttenttu ellekka taw imathay shemppiyaa golliyaa giigissite. Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay hinttenttu woosan taana hinttenttussi guyye zaariide immana gaade qoppay.
\s1 Wurssethaa Sarotaa
\p 
\v 23 Kiristtoosi Yesuusa diraw, taananna qashuwan de7iyaa Eppaafiri neena saro saro gee.
\v 24 Qassi taananna ittippe oothiyaa Marqqoossi, Arisxxirokoosi, Deemaasinne Luqaasi neena saro saro giino.
\p 
\v 25 Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa aadho keekatethay hinttenttu ayyaanaanna gido.
